Uses of Package
net.myorb.math.expressions.tree

  • Packages that use net.myorb.math.expressions.tree 
    Package Description
    net.myorb.math.computational
    Support for computation in multiple dimensions mostly focused on calculus.
    net.myorb.math.expressions
    Core set of classes supporting representation of expressions and their evaluations.
    net.myorb.math.expressions.evaluationstates
    Primitive abstract data layer for the CalcLib environment including functions and operators.
    net.myorb.math.expressions.symbols
    Support for symbols declared in the CalcLib environment including data and operator definitions.
    net.myorb.math.expressions.tree
    Definition of the expression tree that provides efficient execution of evaluation and static storage of expressions as JSON source.
    net.myorb.math.polynomial
    Implementations of algorithms supporting polynomial concepts (family, calculus, fields).
    net.myorb.math.polynomial.families.chebyshev
    Implementations of algorithms supporting Chebyshev polynomial family specifically.
    net.myorb.math.specialfunctions
    Implementations of algorithms supporting special functions (Bessel, Gamma, Ei, other).
